### 3.4 — Fix N+1 query in RSS sources list (P1)

**Severity:** High | **Effort:** 20 min

#### [MODIFY] [rss.routes.ts](file:///c:/Users/MahmoodCenter/Desktop/news-platform-next/server/src/routes/rss.routes.ts)

**Problem:** Sources list loads all feeds with all categories in a single query, but then loops to compute stats — partially an N+1 pattern.

**Fix:**
- Use Prisma's `_count` aggregate in the include
- Remove post-query computation loops
- Add server-side pagination (currently loads ALL sources)

#### Verification
- Manual: With 20+ RSS sources, check response time is <500ms

