### 5.1 — Extract service layer from fat route files (A1)

**Severity:** Critical | **Effort:** 4-6 hours (phased)

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This is the largest refactor. It should be done incrementally — one route file at a time.

#### Phase A: Article Service

#### [NEW] `server/src/services/article.service.ts`

Extract from `article.routes.ts`:
- `createArticle(data, userId)`
- `updateArticle(id, data, userId)`
- `deleteArticle(id, userId)` (soft-delete)
- `publishArticle(id, userId)`
- `getArticles(query)`
