### 5.2 — Add social media tracking table for multi-platform (D6)

**Severity:** High | **Effort:** 1 hour

#### [MODIFY] [schema.prisma](file:///c:/Users/MahmoodCenter/Desktop/news-platform-next/server/prisma/schema.prisma)

- Add `WHATSAPP` to `SocialPlatform` enum
- Create new `SocialPost` model:
```prisma
model SocialPost {
    id              String           @id @default(uuid())
    articleId       String
    platform        SocialPlatform
    status          SocialPostStatus @default(PENDING)
    postId          String?          // Platform-specific post ID
    scheduledAt     DateTime?
    postedAt        DateTime?
    errorMessage    String?          @db.Text
    retryCount      Int              @default(0)
    createdAt       DateTime         @default(now())
    
    @@index([articleId, platform])
    @@index([status])
    @@unique([articleId, platform])
}
```

#### Verification
```bash
cd c:\Users\MahmoodCenter\Desktop\news-platform-next\server
npx prisma migrate dev --name add-social-post-tracking
```

